## Do an Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)


::: {.cell tbl-cap='Grouped summary statistics for the Laminaria dataset, generated directly from code in the chapter source.'}

```{.r .cell-code}
kelp_summary <- kelp |>
  group_by(region) |>
  summarise(
    n = n(),
    mean_stipe = mean(stipe_length),
    mean_blade = mean(blade_length),
    sd_blade = sd(blade_length),
    .groups = "drop"
  )

gt(kelp_summary)
```

